sap.ui.support.helpDescription:
UI5 library: sap.ui.support. A library for the Support Assistant tool.

Overview

The library provides the Support Assistant tool. It enables application developers to check whether their applications are built according to the best practices for building SAPUI5 apps. The tool uses a set of pre-defined rules to check all aspects of an application.

sap.ui.support.name: sap.ui.support

sap.ui.support.ExecutionScope.helpDescription:
Overview

ExecutionScope provides access to internal UI5 objects available for inspection

Usage

Each rule is passed three parameters when executed: check: oIssueManager, oCoreFacade, oScope An ExecutionScope instance is passed to every call of a rule's check method. Available objects are collected depending on the settings passed to Support Assistant's entry point - the analyze method
